summary: This is an email forwarding the 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III' for Project Safe Childhood. It instructs Chiefs and the Project Safe Childhood Coordinator to remind assigned Assistant U.S. Attorneys to update their cases.
keyFacts: The document is an email dated May 24, 2021, regarding Project Safe Childhood.
It references a report titled 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III'.
The email is addressed to 'Chiefs and Project Safe Childhood Coordinator'.
The purpose is to remind assigned Assistant U.S. Attorneys (AUSAs) to update their cases.
The document is administrative in nature, focusing on case management updates for child exploitation and pornography cases.
